Leonardo Tote - Points

Leonardo Tote scores a career high 29 points (2023)

On October 22, 2023, Leonardo Tote set his career high in points in a Italy - LBA Serie A game. That day he scored 29 points in Pesaro's home loss against Scafati, 103-107. He also had 7 rebounds, 1 assist. He shot 9/16 from two, shooting at 56.3% from the field. He also shot 11/12 from the free-throw line.

Leonardo Tote - Rebounds

Leonardo Tote grabs a career high 14 rebounds (2019)

On January 06, 2019, Leonardo Tote set his career high in rebounds in a Italy - Serie A2 Girone EST game. That day he grabbed 14 rebounds in Jesi's road loss against Mantova, 92-66. He also had 13 points, 1 assist, 1 steal and 2 blocks.

Leonardo Tote - Assists

Leonardo Tote gives a career high 5 assists (2019)

On January 30, 2019, Leonardo Tote set his career high in assists in a Italy - Serie A2 Girone EST game. That day he dished 5 assists in Jesi's home win against Piacenza, 96-87. He also had 21 points, 13 rebounds, 1 steal and 2 blocks.

Leonardo Tote - Steals

Leonardo Tote has a career high 4 steals (2016)

On October 23, 2016, Leonardo Tote set his career high in steals in a Italy - Serie A2 game. That day he reached 4 steals in Verona's home win against Trieste, 75-70. He also had 2 points, 3 rebounds.

Leonardo Tote - Blocks

Leonardo Tote blocks a career high 4 shots (2019)

On January 27, 2019, Leonardo Tote tied his career high in blocks in a Italy - Serie A2 Girone EST game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Jesi's home win against Forli, 82-71. He also had 27 points, 6 rebounds.

Leonardo Tote - Efficiency

Leonardo Tote records a career high 36 efficiency rating (2018)

On December 16, 2018, Leonardo Tote set his career high in efficiency in a Italy - Serie A2 Girone EST game. That day he accomplished 36 efficiency in Jesi's home win against Andrea Costa Imola, 113-107. He also had 25 points, 12 rebounds and 2 assists.
